  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5779420/" class="title-link">终结最后的堡垒——评哈耶克《货币的非国家化》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5779420"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/68478247/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68478247/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风灵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-16 10:02:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5779420_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《货币的非国家化》是哈耶克最后一本经济学专著，比起他那些闻名遐迩名垂青史的大作，这本书似乎不那么引人注目。因为它似乎走得太远，太偏激，而“主流经济学家”和“银行家”们不会把它当真。    哈耶克认为，要彻底解决通货膨胀问题，应当让银行自由发行货币，不同的货币在...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
