              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28338769/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p28338769-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">中国人早期用的这个词是啥？贝？刀？币？交子？钞？ </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28338769/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
