              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                中国人早期用的这个词是啥？贝？刀？币？交子？钞？<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p28338769-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
